@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_jckjlr(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v1 = wp.sin((wp.abs(v1 + 0.05) / wp.sin(tmp + 0.63)))
    v2 = wp.exp((wp.sin(v0 + 0.93) / wp.cos(tmp + 0.28)))
    tmp = ((wp.sin(v2 + 0.38) + wp.abs(v2 + 0.55)) + tmp)
    data[tid] = v0
